summary: This is a simple retexture for one of the moons. It replaces it with the funny moon from the mighty boosh, complete with 8 expressions depending on the phase of the moon.
descriptionHtml:
This is a simple retexture for one of the moons. It replaces it with the funny moon from the mighty boosh, complete with 8 expressions depending on the phase of the moon. 

To install, just merge with your skyrim/data folder. Enjoy

**note** the moon is tilted, I textured it this way...idk..i like it.
author: Redman and Rigormortician
